1
00:01:35,700 --> 00:01:39,980
[Veil of Shadows]

2
00:01:39,980 --> 00:01:42,980
[Episode 28]

3
00:02:38,910 --> 00:02:39,600
You Chi.

4
00:02:44,910 --> 00:02:45,560
You Chi?

5
00:03:04,700 --> 00:03:05,390
Wu Shiguang,

6
00:03:06,330 --> 00:03:07,350
ever since we were kids,

7
00:03:08,660 --> 00:03:09,220
I've been

8
00:03:09,220 --> 00:03:10,350
your little tagalong.

9
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:13,560
I was your playmate.

10
00:03:15,160 --> 00:03:16,470
I left home with you

11
00:03:17,750 --> 00:03:18,970
and braved danger with you.

12
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:23,680
Why can't I remember it?

13
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:26,760
I even followed you to the Shilin Sect.

14
00:03:27,950 --> 00:03:29,060
Have you seen Wu Shiguang?

15
00:03:29,540 --> 00:03:30,420
I've got something really fun

16
00:03:30,420 --> 00:03:31,040
to tell him.

17
00:03:31,330 --> 00:03:32,390
Master Dragon Deity?

18
00:03:32,700 --> 00:03:33,680
He's busy.

19
00:03:33,790 --> 00:03:34,850
Don't bother him.

20
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:36,600
He's still got a lot to deal with.

21
00:03:43,370 --> 00:03:45,810
The people at the Shilin Sect are all pretty nice.

22
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,310
You little weasel,

23
00:03:47,580 --> 00:03:49,010
keep that Shilin Sect token on tight.

24
00:03:49,330 --> 00:03:50,560
Or you'll be wiped out.

25
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:56,100
But the Shilin Sect isn't my home.

26
00:03:57,370 --> 00:03:58,330
A weasel demon like me

27
00:03:58,330 --> 00:03:59,060
shouldn't be here.

28
00:04:00,950 --> 00:04:02,180
Is that the Dragon Deity?

29
00:04:02,580 --> 00:04:03,680
- Look. - He has to be.

30
00:04:03,700 --> 00:04:04,510
Even the demon hunter commander

31
00:04:04,580 --> 00:04:05,560
is standing behind him.

32
00:04:05,580 --> 00:04:07,430
- He has to be. - That's right.

33
00:04:07,580 --> 00:04:09,430
Exactly, he must be the Dragon Deity!

34
00:04:10,290 --> 00:04:11,060
Being here,

35
00:04:11,830 --> 00:04:12,830
I feel like I'm in a skin

36
00:04:12,830 --> 00:04:13,930
that doesn't belong to me.

37
00:04:15,040 --> 00:04:15,720
It's uncomfortable.

38
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:20,890
Now you've got

39
00:04:21,080 --> 00:04:22,640
so many demon hunters

40
00:04:22,790 --> 00:04:23,470
following you.

41
00:04:24,910 --> 00:04:25,560
Maybe

42
00:04:26,080 --> 00:04:27,810
you don't really need me anymore.

43
00:04:39,250 --> 00:04:40,140
I need to talk to you.

44
00:04:40,540 --> 00:04:41,640
Commander Li wants to see me.

45
00:04:41,910 --> 00:04:42,890
Let's talk later.

46
00:04:51,020 --> 00:04:57,580
♪Up the hill, arms open wide, we sing♪

47
00:04:57,980 --> 00:05:04,340
♪You and me, we fear not a thing♪

48
00:05:05,780 --> 00:05:12,300
♪Life may sigh, but with our flesh and bone♪

49
00:05:12,740 --> 00:05:18,460
♪We brave the storm, and claim the truths we own♪

50
00:05:20,140 --> 00:05:25,860
♪We brave the storm, and claim the truths we own♪

51
00:05:26,700 --> 00:05:27,390
So

52
00:05:28,870 --> 00:05:29,430
I'm leaving,

53
00:05:29,790 --> 00:05:30,390
Wu Shiguang.

54
00:05:36,370 --> 00:05:37,350
You idiot weasel.

55
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,010
Formless Moon,

56
00:06:03,910 --> 00:06:04,640
hear my command.

57
00:06:08,950 --> 00:06:09,680
Go.

58
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,470
Activate the Nuwa Formation

59
00:06:13,750 --> 00:06:15,970
and reveal the Four Pillars

60
00:06:16,950 --> 00:06:17,810
that uphold the earth.

61
00:06:18,700 --> 00:06:19,850
Yes.

62
00:06:41,700 --> 00:06:42,680
Have you seen You Chi?

63
00:06:51,330 --> 00:06:51,930
Wangyan!

64
00:06:52,330 --> 00:06:52,930
Canyue.

65
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:55,720
Canyue!

66
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:57,970
Canyue.

67
00:06:59,950 --> 00:07:00,680
Stop her.

68
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:03,720
Canyue.

69
00:07:19,410 --> 00:07:19,970
Wangyan,

70
00:07:21,950 --> 00:07:23,180
what happened?

71
00:07:25,250 --> 00:07:26,010
Jiu Ying...

72
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,430
Jiu Ying isn't dead.

73
00:07:38,870 --> 00:07:41,260
He possessed Wuyi.

74
00:07:48,500 --> 00:07:49,470
Do you remember

75
00:07:49,950 --> 00:07:50,760
the four divine trees

76
00:07:50,830 --> 00:07:52,600
that uphold the earth I told you about?

77
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,850
The Tree of Water grew beneath the sea.

78
00:07:55,250 --> 00:07:56,350
Its trunk

79
00:07:56,700 --> 00:07:58,930
is now the throne in Formless Moon's main hall.

80
00:08:02,950 --> 00:08:03,680
Go.

81
00:08:04,500 --> 00:08:05,430
Yes.

82
00:08:09,330 --> 00:08:10,430
The Crying Elm,

83
00:08:10,450 --> 00:08:12,560
now reduced to a broken stump,

84
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:14,890
is the Tree of Earth.

85
00:08:27,620 --> 00:08:28,680
The Firefluff Tree hidden

86
00:08:28,700 --> 00:08:30,100
in the axle of Wei mansion's weaving workshop

87
00:08:30,370 --> 00:08:31,430
is the Tree of Fire.

88
00:08:44,450 --> 00:08:45,220
Why does Jiu Ying

89
00:08:45,250 --> 00:08:46,100
want to destroy

90
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:47,350
the Four Pillars?

91
00:08:47,950 --> 00:08:49,680
He wants the earth to collapse,

92
00:08:49,910 --> 00:08:51,220
all living things to perish,

93
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,260
and this world

94
00:08:54,540 --> 00:08:56,720
to be left with nothing but fear and despair.

95
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,600
Where is the Tree of Metal?

96
00:09:03,410 --> 00:09:05,100
The Shilin Sect's Golden Scale Tree

97
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:08,100
is the Tree of Metal.

98
00:09:09,450 --> 00:09:09,890
Good thing

99
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:11,640
there is the Eternal Formation

100
00:09:12,250 --> 00:09:13,180
keeping them away.

101
00:09:13,700 --> 00:09:14,180
No.

102
00:09:17,250 --> 00:09:18,100
Wuyi

103
00:09:19,660 --> 00:09:21,260
has a Shilin Sect token.

104
00:09:53,510 --> 00:09:54,890
Wu Shiguang, why haven't you come to find me?

105
00:09:56,580 --> 00:09:57,310
If you don't

106
00:09:57,790 --> 00:09:58,460
show up today,

107
00:09:58,460 --> 00:09:59,470
I won't be so easy

108
00:10:00,250 --> 00:10:01,060
to cheer up!

109
00:10:15,750 --> 00:10:16,350
Ye Changsheng,

110
00:10:16,950 --> 00:10:17,970
bring the nearby townsfolk

111
00:10:18,370 --> 00:10:19,410
into the Shilin Sect

112
00:10:19,410 --> 00:10:19,990
for protection.

113
00:10:19,990 --> 00:10:20,560
Yes.

114
00:10:23,290 --> 00:10:23,850
Hurry!

115
00:10:25,290 --> 00:10:26,140
Watch your step!

116
00:10:29,660 --> 00:10:30,470
This way!

117
00:10:30,660 --> 00:10:31,260
Quick!

118
00:10:34,150 --> 00:10:34,890
Keep up!

119
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:39,680
Be careful!

120
00:10:39,750 --> 00:10:40,430
- Hurry! - Go!

121
00:10:43,380 --> 00:10:43,850
Move!

122
00:10:44,330 --> 00:10:45,010
- Go! - Keep up!

123
00:10:45,010 --> 00:10:45,510
Inside!

124
00:10:45,580 --> 00:10:46,140
Go!

125
00:10:56,250 --> 00:10:58,220
If the Four Pillars collapse completely,

126
00:10:59,910 --> 00:11:02,220
heaven and earth, including the Shilin Sect,

127
00:11:02,370 --> 00:11:03,470
will topple.

128
00:11:03,700 --> 00:11:04,970
We have to stop Jiu Ying,

129
00:11:05,950 --> 00:11:06,600
but...

130
00:11:08,790 --> 00:11:09,560
Master Dragon Deity.

131
00:11:11,060 --> 00:11:15,660
♪In this world of black and white, there's always one flower blooming bright♪

132
00:11:15,900 --> 00:11:20,260
♪The weak may bow, but someone always steps ahead♪

133
00:11:20,620 --> 00:11:25,020
♪As the moon shifts, blade-like scales cry out with gleaming edge...♪

134
00:11:27,620 --> 00:11:30,100
My soul I devote. Long live the dragon.

135
00:11:30,140 --> 00:11:34,980
♪We swear to cut down every demon and every fiend...♪

136
00:11:37,500 --> 00:11:38,350
Master Dragon Deity,

137
00:11:39,250 --> 00:11:40,100
we await your orders.

138
00:11:40,100 --> 00:11:44,380
♪We take life and death in stride, with no fear and no sorrow♪

139
00:11:44,420 --> 00:11:47,980
♪We raise our bowls to the sky, hot blood burning, cold tears gleaming♪

140
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:49,140
Members of the Formless Moon

141
00:11:49,330 --> 00:11:51,470
can draw on the elemental power of the Four Pillars.

142
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:52,950
The possessed sisters

143
00:11:52,950 --> 00:11:54,200
will be much stronger

144
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:55,060
and hard to defeat.

145
00:11:57,040 --> 00:11:58,260
Only spells that counter

146
00:11:58,270 --> 00:11:59,390
the pillars' elements

147
00:11:59,450 --> 00:12:00,560
can oppose them.

148
00:12:01,040 --> 00:12:01,850
Mo Yuntan,

149
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:03,760
your artifact, the Spirit Brush,

150
00:12:03,870 --> 00:12:04,680
uses ink-based

151
00:12:05,040 --> 00:12:06,100
water magic.

152
00:12:06,750 --> 00:12:07,560
It can counter fire.

153
00:12:09,540 --> 00:12:10,640
Leave the Firefluff Tree to me.

154
00:12:16,910 --> 00:12:17,660
The Crying Elm

155
00:12:17,660 --> 00:12:19,260
is the oldest tree,

156
00:12:20,040 --> 00:12:21,350
the ancestor of all trees.

157
00:12:42,330 --> 00:12:44,010
My artifact, Golden Resonance,

158
00:12:44,370 --> 00:12:45,140
counters wood.

159
00:12:45,540 --> 00:12:46,100
Perfect.

160
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:55,930
My blade is a divine weapon left behind by a mountain demon.

161
00:12:56,540 --> 00:12:57,930
For centuries, it'd drawn on

162
00:12:58,370 --> 00:13:00,510
the essence of the soil from the peak of Mount Nandang.

163
00:13:00,830 --> 00:13:01,720
Earth counters water.

164
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:03,760
I'll handle the Formless Moon's Tree of Water.

165
00:13:11,540 --> 00:13:13,010
That leaves the Golden Scale Tree.

166
00:13:15,370 --> 00:13:16,060
Hua Qi...

167
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:13,890
What,

168
00:14:14,950 --> 00:14:16,470
are you going to attack your sister?

169
00:14:17,290 --> 00:14:19,220
It's Jiu Ying I'm going to strike at.

170
00:14:21,330 --> 00:14:22,560
Give my sister back!

171
00:14:57,870 --> 00:14:58,470
What happened?

172
00:15:00,540 --> 00:15:01,350
You Chi,

173
00:15:02,750 --> 00:15:03,560
leave.

174
00:15:03,620 --> 00:15:04,220
No way.

175
00:15:04,870 --> 00:15:05,330
How can I leave

176
00:15:05,330 --> 00:15:06,140
when you're like this?

177
00:15:07,120 --> 00:15:07,680
Hua Qi,

178
00:15:07,910 --> 00:15:08,850
I'm no healer.

179
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,220
Is there any way I can help?

180
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:11,640
Yes.

181
00:15:12,580 --> 00:15:13,260
Take my place

182
00:15:14,290 --> 00:15:15,140
and save the Golden Scale Tree.

183
00:15:16,660 --> 00:15:18,260
Save the Golden Scale Tree?

184
00:15:18,620 --> 00:15:19,260
How?

185
00:15:20,250 --> 00:15:20,680
Should I

186
00:15:21,500 --> 00:15:22,600
catch bugs or water it?

187
00:15:39,790 --> 00:15:40,430
Always

188
00:15:40,870 --> 00:15:41,930
keep this token on you.

189
00:15:42,290 --> 00:15:43,060
Otherwise,

190
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:44,010
the ancient formations

191
00:15:44,040 --> 00:15:45,310
all over the Shilin Sect

192
00:15:45,580 --> 00:15:47,890
will reduce you to ashes in an instant.

193
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:55,930
Remember:

194
00:15:56,910 --> 00:15:58,640
no matter what you are

195
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:00,140
or how capable you are,

196
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:02,510
always give it everything you've got

197
00:16:02,910 --> 00:16:04,310
and do your best.

198
00:16:05,450 --> 00:16:06,810
Only then can you have no regrets.

199
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:17,640
A little weasel

200
00:16:17,950 --> 00:16:19,810
thinks he can fight a nine-tailed fox?

201
00:16:24,450 --> 00:16:25,180
Haven't you heard?

202
00:16:26,910 --> 00:16:27,510
Fire counters metal.

203
00:16:29,450 --> 00:16:30,180
Hua Qi,

204
00:16:31,620 --> 00:16:33,390
you're draining your power.

205
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:34,760
Almost done,

206
00:16:35,120 --> 00:16:35,890
Master Dragon Deity.

207
00:16:37,290 --> 00:16:38,310
Hold on a little longer.

208
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:49,560
Wangyan!

209
00:16:58,250 --> 00:16:59,010
Wangyan,

210
00:17:00,330 --> 00:17:02,060
did you think

211
00:17:02,660 --> 00:17:03,850
I couldn't beat you?

212
00:17:53,080 --> 00:17:53,890
Shiguang,

213
00:17:54,950 --> 00:17:56,390
you are the only one in this world

214
00:17:56,660 --> 00:17:57,810
I still can't let go of.

215
00:17:58,830 --> 00:17:59,930
Though I am gone,

216
00:18:00,790 --> 00:18:02,060
the Star Stone remains.

217
00:18:03,040 --> 00:18:04,350
If you find yourself in dire straits one day,

218
00:18:05,040 --> 00:18:06,350
it may yet help you once.

219
00:18:07,500 --> 00:18:08,390
But remember this.

220
00:18:09,370 --> 00:18:10,970
The Star Stone's power is too great.

221
00:18:11,910 --> 00:18:12,890
Do not use it rashly.

222
00:18:13,040 --> 00:18:13,720
Master...

223
00:18:15,330 --> 00:18:16,220
"Heaven and earth tremble.

224
00:18:16,660 --> 00:18:17,510
Chaos fills the world.

225
00:18:18,120 --> 00:18:19,640
An old soul returns against time.

226
00:18:20,200 --> 00:18:21,810
A new moon reshapes the world."

227
00:18:22,500 --> 00:18:23,310
"Heaven and earth tremble.

228
00:18:24,700 --> 00:18:25,760
Chaos fills the world."

229
00:18:26,910 --> 00:18:28,970
The last share of Chi Wen's Dragon Deity's Power

230
00:18:29,950 --> 00:18:31,180
took Ji Ling's heart stone

231
00:18:31,700 --> 00:18:32,970
to the Dragon Abyss.

232
00:18:34,000 --> 00:18:35,600
Perhaps thousands of years from now,

233
00:18:36,200 --> 00:18:37,600
it may take human form.

234
00:18:38,580 --> 00:18:39,930
"An old soul returns against time."

235
00:18:42,250 --> 00:18:43,220
"An old soul returns against time."

236
00:18:44,040 --> 00:18:44,640
Hua Qi.

237
00:18:47,830 --> 00:18:48,600
Go to the Dragon Abyss.

238
00:18:54,200 --> 00:18:55,010
Give me your hand.

239
00:18:59,450 --> 00:19:00,310
Go to the Dragon Abyss.

240
00:19:00,700 --> 00:19:01,680
Use my blood to activate

241
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:03,060
the Star Stone illusion

242
00:19:03,450 --> 00:19:04,560
and bring Ji Ling's

243
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:05,760
heart stone inside.

244
00:19:06,540 --> 00:19:07,220
Go, now.

245
00:19:07,660 --> 00:19:08,310
All right.

246
00:19:08,380 --> 00:19:10,500
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

247
00:19:10,580 --> 00:19:15,700
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

248
00:19:16,020 --> 00:19:18,220
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

249
00:19:18,340 --> 00:19:23,140
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

250
00:19:23,620 --> 00:19:25,740
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

251
00:19:25,780 --> 00:19:30,660
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies...♪

252
00:19:31,450 --> 00:19:32,140
This...

253
00:19:32,870 --> 00:19:34,140
isn't my limit yet.

254
00:19:34,420 --> 00:19:39,980
♪Let's gaze above♪

255
00:19:41,790 --> 00:19:43,100
Do my best

256
00:19:45,000 --> 00:19:46,220
and leave no regrets!

257
00:19:51,000 --> 00:19:52,640
You only know fire counters metal.

258
00:19:53,620 --> 00:19:54,600
But do you know

259
00:19:54,950 --> 00:19:57,260
that ice counters fire?

260
00:20:10,580 --> 00:20:12,700
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

261
00:20:12,780 --> 00:20:17,900
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

262
00:20:18,220 --> 00:20:20,420
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

263
00:20:20,540 --> 00:20:25,340
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

264
00:20:25,820 --> 00:20:27,940
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

265
00:20:27,980 --> 00:20:32,860
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

266
00:20:33,140 --> 00:20:36,380
♪Stay with me♪

267
00:20:36,620 --> 00:20:41,020
♪Let's gaze above♪

268
00:20:41,020 --> 00:20:43,060
♪It's your light, your storms♪

269
00:20:43,100 --> 00:20:48,140
♪Your watchful eyes, that set the night alight♪

270
00:20:48,260 --> 00:20:51,540
♪And lead me♪

271
00:20:51,740 --> 00:20:56,620
♪Sailing afar♪

272
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:29,220
A fleeting moment in the mortal world

273
00:21:29,870 --> 00:21:30,930
is a thousand years in the illusion.

274
00:21:31,790 --> 00:21:32,810
Master Dragon Deity,

275
00:21:33,830 --> 00:21:35,180
I will bring Ji Ling back.

276
00:21:45,450 --> 00:21:46,260
Your weapon's gone,

277
00:21:47,160 --> 00:21:48,260
and you still won't give up?

278
00:21:48,830 --> 00:21:49,640
The blade's gone,

279
00:21:51,450 --> 00:21:52,510
but I'm still here.

280
00:21:52,700 --> 00:21:54,560
Today, I am going to defeat you!

281
00:22:08,620 --> 00:22:09,390
Who says

282
00:22:10,500 --> 00:22:11,260
a weasel

283
00:22:12,540 --> 00:22:13,930
can't beat a nine-tailed fox?

284
00:22:27,910 --> 00:22:28,680
Wu Shiguang,

285
00:22:31,040 --> 00:22:31,850
this time,

286
00:22:34,120 --> 00:22:34,640
I...

287
00:22:34,950 --> 00:22:36,060
I didn't

288
00:22:38,040 --> 00:22:39,180
hold you back.

289
00:22:47,700 --> 00:22:48,640
You'd better not

290
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:51,140
lock me

291
00:22:51,450 --> 00:22:53,100
inside the Cosmic Pouch again.

292
00:24:16,620 --> 00:24:22,260
♪Clad in golden scales, I gaze from the valley high♪

293
00:24:22,700 --> 00:24:28,860
♪Wiping away the dark to let the moonlight shine♪

294
00:24:29,300 --> 00:24:30,700
♪Through all joys and sorrows♪

295
00:24:30,860 --> 00:24:32,420
♪Bitter and sweet♪

296
00:24:32,620 --> 00:24:35,780
♪The moon stays by my side♪

297
00:24:36,220 --> 00:24:42,020
♪Its light is my most precious scale♪

298
00:24:49,100 --> 00:24:54,620
♪The moon accompanies me as I roam the mortal world♪

299
00:25:01,860 --> 00:25:09,380
♪She looks at me and says, you're not alone tonight♪

300
00:25:23,120 --> 00:25:23,680
"An old soul..."

301
00:25:26,740 --> 00:25:27,450
[The old dragon falls. The new dragon rises.]

302
00:25:27,450 --> 00:25:28,160
[Heaven and earth tremble. Chaos fills the world.]

303
00:25:28,160 --> 00:25:29,140
[An old soul returns against time.]
"Returns against time."

304
00:25:29,140 --> 00:25:29,780
[A new moon reshapes the world.]

305
00:25:32,870 --> 00:25:33,640
You're back.

306
00:25:34,830 --> 00:25:35,680
I am.

307
00:25:37,410 --> 00:25:38,140
And

308
00:25:39,950 --> 00:25:40,890
so are they.

309
00:25:53,060 --> 00:25:58,980
♪If you're the moon, I'll be falling snow...♪

310
00:26:04,750 --> 00:26:05,470
Master.

311
00:26:07,140 --> 00:26:13,020
♪I truly miss the taste of your tears♪

312
00:26:13,300 --> 00:26:13,900
♪So please♪

313
00:26:14,180 --> 00:26:19,780
♪Don't say goodbye before the sun fades from view♪

314
00:26:20,380 --> 00:26:20,980
♪So please♪

315
00:26:21,260 --> 00:26:26,020
♪Don't say goodbye before the sun♪

316
00:26:26,040 --> 00:26:27,220
Why are you all back?

317
00:26:28,370 --> 00:26:30,180
Because Ji Ling has already awakened the people

318
00:26:30,910 --> 00:26:31,760
of the Formless Moon.

319
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:34,760
Wake.

320
00:26:40,060 --> 00:26:45,220
♪Asking the night why it keeps me bound♪

321
00:26:47,380 --> 00:26:54,380
♪Has anyone heard my call?♪

322
00:26:54,620 --> 00:26:59,700
♪Like a feather waiting for its final fall♪

323
00:27:00,500 --> 00:27:06,580
♪I would buy osmanthus and wine again, but I'm no longer young♪

324
00:27:07,420 --> 00:27:13,380
♪A speck of dust weighs heavy on my heart and throat♪

325
00:27:14,260 --> 00:27:21,300
♪I pace back and forth, counting footprints, too afraid to look up♪

326
00:27:21,420 --> 00:27:27,740
♪Trapped like rainwater in a lake♪

327
00:27:27,780 --> 00:27:34,300
♪So many dawns and dusks in pouring rain♪

328
00:27:34,660 --> 00:27:37,260
♪Twilight weighs down beyond our sight♪

329
00:27:37,260 --> 00:27:41,140
♪Trapping us small souls so tight♪

330
00:27:41,660 --> 00:27:48,980
♪So many lives, like a speck of dust♪

331
00:27:49,380 --> 00:27:55,620
♪Yet every tiny me speaks loud and just♪

332
00:28:30,540 --> 00:28:30,930
Wang,

333
00:28:32,330 --> 00:28:34,250
the Four Pillars have been corrupted

334
00:28:34,250 --> 00:28:35,810
by the evil energy inside Jiu Ying.

335
00:28:37,580 --> 00:28:38,420
Only by sacrificing

336
00:28:38,420 --> 00:28:40,180
the Formless Moon power within us

337
00:28:41,250 --> 00:28:43,220
can we cleanse that evil energy.

338
00:28:44,120 --> 00:28:45,890
The wrong was ours.

339
00:28:46,950 --> 00:28:48,680
Let us make amends ourselves.

340
00:28:49,620 --> 00:28:50,220
Wang,

341
00:28:50,830 --> 00:28:51,430
we leave

342
00:28:51,950 --> 00:28:52,760
the rest to you.

343
00:28:54,000 --> 00:28:54,890
Save this world

344
00:28:55,500 --> 00:28:57,430
we have guarded for a millennium.

345
00:29:02,000 --> 00:29:02,560
What is it?

346
00:29:03,910 --> 00:29:04,930
What did the Moon Summoning Pearl say?

347
00:29:06,580 --> 00:29:07,140
Nothing.

348
00:29:08,160 --> 00:29:09,850
The sisters have all come to their senses.

349
00:29:12,290 --> 00:29:13,760
They're repairing the Four Pillars.

350
00:29:17,700 --> 00:29:18,810
The collapse has stopped.

351
00:29:20,830 --> 00:29:22,260
Looks like they're all restored.

352
00:29:56,080 --> 00:29:57,310
I'll check on the Golden Scale Tree.

353
00:29:57,620 --> 00:29:58,430
Be careful.

354
00:29:59,540 --> 00:30:00,310
I've got it covered here.

355
00:30:26,790 --> 00:30:28,560
You're still alive?

356
00:30:29,620 --> 00:30:30,680
Too bad Lu Wuyi thought

357
00:30:30,950 --> 00:30:32,350
you were truly dead.

358
00:30:32,620 --> 00:30:33,930
She was so heartbroken

359
00:30:35,120 --> 00:30:36,510
that even her soul

360
00:30:36,540 --> 00:30:38,060
scattered into nothing.

361
00:30:39,160 --> 00:30:39,850
Jiu Ying,

362
00:30:41,160 --> 00:30:42,310
you killed Wu.

363
00:30:44,330 --> 00:30:45,100
Today,

364
00:30:46,080 --> 00:30:48,600
I will make sure your soul is utterly destroyed.

365
00:31:02,290 --> 00:31:03,180
Lu Wuyi,

366
00:31:04,580 --> 00:31:06,470
you woke up again?

367
00:31:06,750 --> 00:31:07,760
I told you,

368
00:31:09,540 --> 00:31:10,890
the one who should get out

369
00:31:12,370 --> 00:31:13,390
is you.

370
00:31:17,080 --> 00:31:17,640
Wu.

371
00:31:21,620 --> 00:31:22,640
Ji,

372
00:31:23,950 --> 00:31:26,510
Jiu Ying has been trying to take control.

373
00:31:27,620 --> 00:31:28,600
Ji,

374
00:31:29,700 --> 00:31:30,560
do it.

375
00:31:31,700 --> 00:31:32,680
Kill me.

376
00:31:38,120 --> 00:31:40,260
Since I was created, I've been controlled

377
00:31:41,450 --> 00:31:42,390
my whole life.

378
00:31:44,700 --> 00:31:45,970
This time,

379
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:50,010
I want to be my true self.

380
00:31:52,620 --> 00:31:53,470
Help me,

381
00:31:55,330 --> 00:31:56,220
Ji.

382
00:32:12,540 --> 00:32:13,140
Form up.

383
00:32:16,620 --> 00:32:17,510
Qisha of the Southern Dipper.

384
00:32:17,620 --> 00:32:18,430
Tiantong of the Southern Dipper.

385
00:32:18,580 --> 00:32:19,260
Pojun of the Northern Dipper.

386
00:32:19,910 --> 00:32:20,470
In positions!

387
00:32:34,580 --> 00:32:39,060
♪In this world of black and white, there's always one flower blooming bright♪

388
00:32:39,300 --> 00:32:43,660
♪The weak may bow, but someone always steps ahead♪

389
00:32:44,020 --> 00:32:48,420
♪As the moon shifts, blade-like scales cry out with gleaming edge♪

390
00:32:48,820 --> 00:32:53,020
♪A vow of double flowers, to guard tomorrow together♪

391
00:32:53,020 --> 00:32:54,980
♪Moon and scales shine in radiant splendor♪

392
00:32:55,180 --> 00:32:57,540
♪As the winds rise, dragons and foxes cry in strife♪

393
00:32:57,580 --> 00:33:01,980
♪At the world's end, the destined soul rides proud and free♪

394
00:33:02,540 --> 00:33:04,820
♪Soaring high on the wind♪

395
00:33:04,980 --> 00:33:07,140
♪I will gather the stars and cradle the moon for you♪

396
00:33:07,300 --> 00:33:08,820
♪Bearing treasured fragments of wonder♪

397
00:33:08,940 --> 00:33:12,780
♪Behold the moon and scales in radiant splendor♪

398
00:33:14,420 --> 00:33:17,180
♪There's always one flower blooming bright♪

399
00:33:17,420 --> 00:33:21,780
♪The weak may bow, but someone always steps ahead♪

400
00:33:22,140 --> 00:33:26,540
♪As the moon shifts, blade-like scales cry out with gleaming edge♪

401
00:33:26,940 --> 00:33:31,580
♪A vow of double flowers, to guard tomorrow together♪

402
00:34:42,620 --> 00:34:43,310
Master.

403
00:35:08,330 --> 00:35:08,910
You Chi.

404
00:35:09,860 --> 00:35:10,540
Wangyan,

405
00:35:11,410 --> 00:35:12,310
I did great

406
00:35:13,870 --> 00:35:14,760
this time.

407
00:35:17,160 --> 00:35:17,890
She said

408
00:35:18,790 --> 00:35:19,390
a weasel

409
00:35:20,750 --> 00:35:22,060
couldn't beat a nine-tailed fox,

410
00:35:22,870 --> 00:35:23,560
but

411
00:35:24,120 --> 00:35:24,890
look,

412
00:35:26,330 --> 00:35:27,890
I still beat her.

413
00:35:32,660 --> 00:35:34,180
I helped, didn't I?

414
00:35:35,330 --> 00:35:36,100
Oh, right.

415
00:35:36,750 --> 00:35:37,470
Look.

416
00:35:38,370 --> 00:35:39,260
I was

417
00:35:41,080 --> 00:35:42,140
so smart this time.

418
00:35:44,750 --> 00:35:45,640
Wu Shiguang

419
00:35:46,080 --> 00:35:47,100
won't get to call me

420
00:35:47,120 --> 00:35:48,180
an idiot again.

421
00:35:49,910 --> 00:35:50,810
Do you know?

422
00:35:51,620 --> 00:35:52,350
Wu Shiguang

423
00:35:52,870 --> 00:35:53,890
always says

424
00:35:54,330 --> 00:35:55,760
that when danger comes,

425
00:35:57,830 --> 00:35:59,890
I'm the type to dig a hole and hide in it.

426
00:36:00,580 --> 00:36:01,850
Before you came,

427
00:36:03,000 --> 00:36:04,350
I was so sad,

428
00:36:05,750 --> 00:36:07,850
because I was going to die here alone,

429
00:36:09,700 --> 00:36:11,100
and no one would ever know.

430
00:36:12,660 --> 00:36:13,810
Wu Shiguang

431
00:36:14,620 --> 00:36:16,310
must think I ran away again.

432
00:36:20,060 --> 00:36:20,510
Oh,

433
00:36:20,540 --> 00:36:21,310
right.

434
00:36:21,950 --> 00:36:23,810
Remember to tell him

435
00:36:24,450 --> 00:36:25,220
that I...

436
00:36:27,000 --> 00:36:27,850
I really...

437
00:36:30,120 --> 00:36:32,180
really did my best.

438
00:36:32,700 --> 00:36:33,510
I did...

439
00:36:34,830 --> 00:36:36,560
I did my best.

440
00:36:40,250 --> 00:36:41,100
You Chi.

441
00:36:41,370 --> 00:36:42,010
You Chi!

442
00:36:42,900 --> 00:36:46,780
♪And through the winter cold, it stayed with me♪

443
00:36:49,060 --> 00:36:55,580
♪Up the hill, arms open wide, we sing♪

444
00:36:55,900 --> 00:37:02,300
♪You and me, we fear not a thing♪

445
00:37:03,780 --> 00:37:10,260
♪Life may sigh, but with our flesh and bone♪

446
00:37:10,660 --> 00:37:16,220
♪We brave the storm, and claim the truths we own♪

447
00:37:18,540 --> 00:37:25,020
♪Life may sigh, but with our flesh and bone♪

448
00:37:25,500 --> 00:37:31,380
♪We brave the storm, and claim the truths we own♪

449
00:38:24,410 --> 00:38:25,140
How?

450
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:28,350
Lu Wuyi's soul was unusually resilient.

451
00:38:29,160 --> 00:38:30,240
I was never able to find

452
00:38:30,240 --> 00:38:31,760
a way to erase it completely.

453
00:38:32,120 --> 00:38:33,310
I should thank you,

454
00:38:33,500 --> 00:38:34,350
Wu Shiguang.

455
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:36,470
With your Dragon Deity's Power,

456
00:38:37,250 --> 00:38:38,290
you wiped out

457
00:38:38,290 --> 00:38:40,100
the last trace of her soul

458
00:38:41,160 --> 00:38:43,430
and let me own this body completely.

459
00:38:46,950 --> 00:38:49,220
Why won't Lu Wuyi's body die?

460
00:38:52,380 --> 00:38:53,100
[The old dragon falls. The new dragon rises.]

461
00:38:53,100 --> 00:38:53,820
[Heaven and earth tremble. Chaos fills the world.]

462
00:38:53,820 --> 00:38:55,100
[An old soul returns against time. A new moon reshapes the world.]

463
00:38:57,120 --> 00:38:58,510
The Oracle Stone is missing a piece.

464
00:38:59,000 --> 00:38:59,890
The Oracle Stone!

465
00:39:00,540 --> 00:39:01,390
Besides a fragment

466
00:39:01,660 --> 00:39:03,430
of Jiu Ying's spirit,

467
00:39:03,950 --> 00:39:05,760
a fragment of the Oracle Stone is in her too.

468
00:39:08,120 --> 00:39:09,310
Wu's body

469
00:39:09,540 --> 00:39:12,060
was made from the flesh and blood of nine-tailed foxes.

470
00:39:12,910 --> 00:39:14,090
It has the power of rebirth

471
00:39:14,090 --> 00:39:15,720
granted by the Formless Moon.

472
00:39:16,750 --> 00:39:18,670
If she also has the Oracle Stone's

473
00:39:18,670 --> 00:39:20,010
ever-living divine power,

474
00:39:21,200 --> 00:39:21,720
then...

475
00:39:27,200 --> 00:39:28,640
Is there really no other way?

476
00:39:31,500 --> 00:39:32,760
"An old soul returns against time.

477
00:39:34,660 --> 00:39:35,970
A new moon reshapes the world."

478
00:39:40,000 --> 00:39:40,720
A new moon...

479
00:39:52,700 --> 00:39:53,930
There is still one way.

480
00:39:56,830 --> 00:39:57,850
And it's the only way.

481
00:40:02,000 --> 00:40:02,970
You've thought of it too.

482
00:40:04,620 --> 00:40:05,390
What is it?

483
00:40:08,790 --> 00:40:09,890
Turn back time

484
00:40:10,830 --> 00:40:11,930
and go back to the past

485
00:40:13,910 --> 00:40:15,720
to stop Lu Wuyi from ever being born.

486
00:40:16,830 --> 00:40:17,640
In other words,

487
00:40:19,450 --> 00:40:21,640
erase Lu Wuyi's existence completely.

488
00:40:27,580 --> 00:40:29,310
Didn't Lonescale tell you?

489
00:40:30,660 --> 00:40:33,350
The recent past of a few days can be changed.

490
00:40:34,750 --> 00:40:37,060
But Lu Wuyi was born 50 years ago.

491
00:40:38,290 --> 00:40:40,560
To go back that far

492
00:40:40,950 --> 00:40:42,100
and change the past?

493
00:40:44,330 --> 00:40:45,430
A fool's dream.

494
00:40:47,660 --> 00:40:49,010
"A new moon reshapes the world."

495
00:40:50,040 --> 00:40:51,060
Since the Oracle Stone

496
00:40:51,370 --> 00:40:53,060
gave such a prophecy,

497
00:40:53,950 --> 00:40:54,930
it means

498
00:40:58,040 --> 00:40:59,560
this is destined to happen.

499
00:41:02,830 --> 00:41:04,390
I was a fallen star from beyond the heavens.

500
00:41:05,950 --> 00:41:07,720
I'm not bound by the laws of this world.

501
00:41:11,580 --> 00:41:12,930
There was one question

502
00:41:14,000 --> 00:41:15,470
I spent my whole life pondering.

503
00:41:16,790 --> 00:41:18,220
Even after bitter years of cultivation,

504
00:41:18,830 --> 00:41:20,060
I could never solve it.

505
00:41:21,290 --> 00:41:23,350
You bear extraordinary power from beyond the heavens.

506
00:41:23,750 --> 00:41:24,470
Slaughter

507
00:41:24,910 --> 00:41:26,680
is not your only choice.

508
00:41:27,700 --> 00:41:29,010
I hope that one day,

509
00:41:29,500 --> 00:41:31,970
you'll find the true meaning of coming to this world

510
00:41:32,330 --> 00:41:33,760
after crossing

511
00:41:34,410 --> 00:41:35,600
countless galaxies.

512
00:41:36,790 --> 00:41:37,600
For the past thousand years,

513
00:41:37,660 --> 00:41:38,760
I have asked myself

514
00:41:41,040 --> 00:41:43,180
why I came to this world

515
00:41:44,830 --> 00:41:45,560
and what

516
00:41:47,870 --> 00:41:49,720
I could do for it.

517
00:41:51,290 --> 00:41:52,720
Now I understand.

518
00:41:54,620 --> 00:41:56,100
After I crossed the galaxies

519
00:41:56,700 --> 00:41:57,970
and came to this world,

520
00:41:59,290 --> 00:42:00,510
I brought disaster upon it

521
00:42:01,290 --> 00:42:02,510
and gave rise to Jiu Ying.

522
00:42:07,120 --> 00:42:08,100
So

523
00:42:09,750 --> 00:42:11,640
it should be me who brings him to an end

524
00:42:13,090 --> 00:42:14,620
and saves this world.

525
00:42:31,540 --> 00:42:32,700
♪It's your light♪

526
00:42:32,900 --> 00:42:34,780
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

527
00:42:34,940 --> 00:42:38,060
♪That set the night alight♪

528
00:42:38,420 --> 00:42:44,940
♪And lead me through the fight♪

529
00:42:46,700 --> 00:42:48,580
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

530
00:42:49,020 --> 00:42:53,460
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

531
00:42:54,260 --> 00:42:55,940
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

532
00:42:56,100 --> 00:43:01,500
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

533
00:43:02,260 --> 00:43:07,660
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

534
00:43:09,980 --> 00:43:16,020
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

535
00:43:16,980 --> 00:43:19,140
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

536
00:43:19,420 --> 00:43:24,260
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

537
00:43:24,620 --> 00:43:26,940
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

538
00:43:27,140 --> 00:43:32,220
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

539
00:43:32,460 --> 00:43:34,460
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

540
00:43:34,740 --> 00:43:39,100
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

541
00:43:40,100 --> 00:43:47,060
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

542
00:44:03,620 --> 00:44:06,580
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

543
00:44:07,660 --> 00:44:11,060
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

544
00:44:11,860 --> 00:44:14,380
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

545
00:44:14,620 --> 00:44:17,700
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

546
00:44:18,100 --> 00:44:20,420
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

547
00:44:20,940 --> 00:44:25,340
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

548
00:44:25,580 --> 00:44:27,740
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

549
00:44:28,140 --> 00:44:33,100
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

550
00:44:33,340 --> 00:44:34,500
♪It's your light♪

551
00:44:34,700 --> 00:44:36,540
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

552
00:44:36,740 --> 00:44:39,860
♪That set the night alight♪

553
00:44:40,620 --> 00:44:50,060
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
